<paragraph blockId="130.[684,1212,1215,1735]" pageId="130" pageNumber="130">
IDENTIFICATION: 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Desmarest" baseAuthorityYear="1819" box="[911,1134,1380,1404]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Eptesicus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="130" pageNumber="130" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="brasiliensis">
<emphasis box="[911,1134,1380,1404]" italics="true" pageId="130" pageNumber="130">Eptesicus brasiliensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is distinguished from other Neotropical congeners by its medium size (forearm 
<quantity box="[986,1112,1446,1470]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.35" metricValueMax="4.7" metricValueMin="4.0" pageId="130" pageNumber="130" unit="mm" value="43.5" valueMax="47.0" valueMin="40.0">40–47 mm</quantity>
, greatest length of skull 
<quantity box="[855,979,1479,1503]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.7" metricValueMax="1.8" metricValueMin="1.6" pageId="130" pageNumber="130" unit="mm" value="17.0" valueMax="18.0" valueMin="16.0">16–18 mm</quantity>
), relatively short (&lt;
<quantity metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.0" pageId="130" pageNumber="130" unit="mm" value="7.0">7 mm</quantity>
) dorsal fur, brownish ventral fur, U-shaped nasal opening, and inflated rostrum (Davis, 1966; 
<collectingRegion box="[752,847,1578,1602]" country="Venezuela" name="Miranda" pageId="130" pageNumber="130">Miranda</collectingRegion>
et al., 2006; Davis and Gardner, 2008; López-Baucells et al., 2018). Descriptions and measurements of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Desmarest" baseAuthorityYear="1819" box="[939,1091,1644,1668]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Eptesicus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="130" pageNumber="130" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="brasiliensis">
<emphasis box="[939,1091,1644,1668]" italics="true" pageId="130" pageNumber="130">E. brasiliensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
were provided by Davis (1965, 1966), Barquez et al. (1999), Lim et al. (2005), 
<collectingRegion box="[970,1064,1710,1734]" country="Venezuela" name="Miranda" pageId="130" pageNumber="130">Miranda</collectingRegion>
et al. (2006),
</paragraph>
